d break the\ndegeneracy between the identified RM intervals. The most reasonable of them\nturned out to be RM = 9-17 rad/m^2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2006 15:50:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Jun 2006 17:36:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
