ress the need to go beyond simple\nmodifications of evolution by developing proper theoretical tools that\nimplement such recently discussed ingredients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2006 15:50:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2006 15:38:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 May 2006 12:11:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
